<br>
A guild is trying to grow, a guild is making an attempt at &quot;becoming uber&quot; what problems does that guild face? Trakanon, Sky plane, woushi? Nope, Uber mobs are hardly the problem give a guild with the right size enough time and they can handle it. The largest problem that plagues this server is greed, we are all guilty of it. &quot;Let me roll on that tranq staff because I can sell it and get good stuff.&quot; <br>
