<br>
I leave you with this final statement to all of you in non uber guilds. <br>
<br>
We all have friends in uber guilds they can be close they can be just people you say hi to. The fact remains as much as they care about you their guild could give a crap about you. Big Brother doesn't care about you, Big Brother just cares that you offer them an easy answer to the &quot;how do we get our god drops and epic quest items.&quot; They will always be there waiting to &quot;help&quot; you but they will also always be there to hold you down as well. <br>
<br>
Thank you.<br>
